videos.description: ASU QB Manny connects with Brandon Aiyuk for a 51-yard pass that leads to a Sun Devils' field goal.
videos.headline: Aiyuk 51-yard catch sets up ASU FG

videos.description: ASU QB Manning Wilkins runs, then  fumbles which is forced by Stanford's Bobby Okereke and recovered by Thomas Booker.
videos.headline: Booker recover ASU fumble

videos.description: ASU Eno Benjamin makes a one-handed grab, then runs for 29-yards to give ASU a first down late in the 2nd quarter.
videos.headline: Benjamin's one-handed catch gives ASU a 1st down

videos.description: In field goal range, Arizona State runs a trick play where N'Keal Harry's pass is intercepted by Stanford's Sean Barton late in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Barton's interception stalls potential ASU scoring drive

videos.description: Stanford RB Bryce Love loves left and gets brought down awkwardly, then would limp to the bench.
videos.headline: Love limps to the sideline

videos.description: Stanford RB Cameron Scarlett drives in a 1-yard touchdown to extend the lead to 20-6.
videos.headline: Scarlett punches in 1-yard TD

videos.description: Manny Wilkins pass is intercepted by Stanford's Paulson Adebo for ASU's third turnover of the night.
videos.headline: ASU records third turnover
